The announcement that you have been waiting for - @tigerjackieshroff is coming to launch @asicsindia store at Ambience Mall, Gurugram on the 22nd of June. What’s more? You've got a chance to meet him. IN PERSON.

All you've got to do is -
• Copy the dance move shown in the reel
• Upload your version with #TigerMovesInASICS and tag us @tigerjackieshroff and @asicsindia 
 
The best entries stand a chance to meet Tiger Shroff.
 
#ASICSIN #ASICSportStyle #SoundMindSoundBody #LiveUplifted
Thank you mothers for all the love you have showered on us all these years. We wish all mums in the world a Happy Mothers Day from team Ambience Malls. #ambiencemall #mothersday #mothersdaygift

Today is International dance day & it is celebrated every year on April 29th to promote arts and culture & raise awareness on various forms of dance. On this occasion, we have brought artists & dancers from Bhangra Sway, Mudra dance academy and Star dance academy who are performing on some popular dance forms like Bharatnatyam, Ghoomar, Bhangra, Tango, Bachta and Hiphop for keeping up with the spirit of celebration. 
We wish a very happy International Dance Day to all the dancers worldwide. 
#ambiencemall #danceday #internationaldanceday

@zambarofficial is an experiential restaurant and promises to show the different facets of Southern India through vibrant delicacies and an authentic menu. Located on the third floor at Ambience Mall Gurgaon and a must visit restaurant when you’re craving authentic South Indian fare. #ambiencemall #foodie #food #foodporn  #foodblogger

A unique kitchen concept that provides hundred percent vegetarian Gujrati- Marwari cuisine in an unlimited thali type format. @Manbhavan thali
literally means pleasing the mind and they di it with the way of quality food and quality service. Visit today at Ambience Mall Gurgaon. #ambiencemall #foodie #foodporn #foodblogger

Get proper Punjabi highway fare from the original @dhaba1986. From the legendary Baalti meat to finger licking chicken curry, get a taste of the best of North Indian specialities today. Visit at Ambience Mall Gurgaon. #ambiencemall #dineinambience #foodie #foodblogger #foodporn
